data.description: Welcome to this beautifully well-maintained and elegant 2-story brick home, featuring modern upgrades and eco-friendly lifestyle features. This home includes 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage. Sophistication is evident throughout, with beautiful chandeliers, an upgraded front door, and  low-maintenance vinyl flooring. The seamless flow of the open-concept design connects the kitchen, dining, and living areas, creating a perfect environment for gatherings. The heart of the home is the kitchen, a chef's delight, featuring stainless steel appliances, a large island for culinary adventures, and an upgraded elegant backsplash that enhances the aesthetic appeal, complete with a water filtration system for drinking water. Enjoy the convenience of the main-level primary bedroom suite, which includes bay windows and spacious walk-in closets, along with a double vanity, walk-in shower, and bathtub. Upstairs, three additional bedrooms provide ample space for family or guests, each room exuding comfort and style. The upper level also boasts a spacious loft area, perfect for a game room, home office, or family den, offering flexibility and extra living space. Step outside to the large, newly-stained, fenced backyard where an oversized extended patio with an outdoor kitchen awaits. This outdoor haven, complete with a roof and remote-controlled patio shade, is ideal for entertaining or simply enjoying quiet evenings. The home has the eco-friendly addition of fully paid solar panels, providing energy efficiency and cost savings. The practicality of this home extends to the front and back yards, both equipped with a sprinkler system for easy maintenance. Rounding off the home's features is the garage, complete with a 220 outlet for electric vehicle charging, adding convenience for the modern homeowner. This splendid home is conveniently located minutes away from major highways 1604 and i-10, Randolph AFB, shopping centers, and top-rated schools, offering a perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and eco-friendly living. Schedule your home tour now!
